一名法官做出了有利于政府的裁决，认为该平台藐视法庭，因为该平台拒绝遵守规定，直到法院规定的最后期限过后。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:28;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-fined-for-belatedly-complying-with-search-warrant-for-donald-trumps-account-173745495.html"><strong><ins>继续阅读。</ins></strong></a></p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:29;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/biden-signs-executive-order-restricting-investment-in-chinese-tech-companies-230728855.html"><ins>拜登签署限制对中国科技公司投资的行政命令</ins></a></h2><h3>这包括半导体、量子计算和人工智能。</h3><p></p><p>拜登总统签署<a data-i13n="cpos:30;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/biden-signs-executive-order-restricting-investment-in-chinese-tech-companies-230728855.html"><ins>行政命令，限制美国对中国科技行业多个领域的投资</ins></a>。其目的是解决半导体、量子计算和人工智能等敏感技术跨境流动带来的安全问题。白宫表示，这些技术如果以某种方式开发，可能会对国家安全构成威胁。它补充说，这些规则的范围足够窄，只针对可能产生安全影响的技术，而不是全面禁止这些保护伞下的所有技术。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:31;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/biden-signs-executive-order-restricting-investment-in-chinese-tech-companies-230728855.html"><strong><ins>继续阅读。</ins></strong></a></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-which-samsung-foldable-should-you-buy-111537694.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-which-samsung-foldable-should-you-buy-111537694.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 08d1fa25-0483-41d6-9997-2b747cf48528</guid><dc:creator>丹尼尔·库珀</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 10 Aug 2023 11:15:37 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691662547</ingested><modified> 2023-08-10T10:15:58+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Daniel Cooper]]></category><media:content height="1166" mediu