.html">对华为</a>实施了重大限制。白宫还限制向中国公司出售<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/us-trade-restrictions-chinese-miitary-ai-supercomputer-companies-082453795.html">超级计算技术</a>，并试图阻止中国获得先进的<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="http://v/">芯片制造</a>设备。拜登政府还向 TikTok 的中国所有者<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-us-government-is-trying-to-force-bytedance-to-sell-tiktok-005751763.html">字节跳动施压</a>，要求其出售这款受欢迎的应用程序。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/biden-signs-executive-order-restricting-investment-in-chinese-tech-companies-230728855.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/biden-signs-executive-order-restricting-investment-in-chinese-tech-companies-230728855.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> ee495673-2156-43a5-8a84-6d7651727ae1</guid><dc:creator>卡丽莎·贝尔</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 09 Aug 2023 23:07:28 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691672446</ingested><modified> 2023-08-10T13:00:58+00:00</modified><category><![CDATA[Government]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Karissa Bell]]></category><media:content height="3498" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/2ad3be50-3708-11ee-a6fb-f495aaa2625a" width="5248"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3498" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/2ad3be50-3708-11ee-a6fb-f495aaa2625a" width