lecom/meta-plans-retention-hooks-threads-more-than-half-users-leave-app-2023-07-28/">表示</a>，该功能可以被视为 Meta 精心设计的“保留驱动钩子”之一，以确保“Instagram 应用程序上的用户可以看到重要的线程”。据称，该策略与有关该新兴平台在不到一周内<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/metas-threads-races-to-100-million-users-in-under-a-week-070740016.html">增加了 1 亿多用户</a>后<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/threads-users-are-already-spending-less-time-in-the-app-182738755.html">参与度下降的报道</a>有关。据报道，扎克伯格将这种下降描述为“正常”，并且随着 Meta 继续充实 7 月初<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/metas-instagram-linked-twitter-rival-threads-could-arrive-on-july-6th-063129168.html">推出的</a>社交渠道，预计保留率将会增长。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/cbfb09c0-36ed-11ee-9fff-6c4db0ec6a33" style="height:1080px;width:1800px;" alt="显示 Meta Threads 应用程序的新替代文本功能的三个屏幕截图。左：图像，中：空白替代文本，右：起草替代文本。" data-uuid="c5cb7773-e663-3dc8-a714-d34e578bfce3"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">元</div></figure><p>同时，自定义替代文本选项是一项辅助功能，允许 Threads 用户在上传之前为照片和视频添加（或编辑现有的自动生成的）替代文本。新的提及按钮使您可以更轻松地在 Threads 帖子中标记个人资料。最后，该平台使您可以更轻松地在 Mastodon 等联邦平台上验证您的身份。 Instagram 负责人 Adam Mosseri 今天<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.threads.net/@mosseri/post/Cvu2fDiLZve">发帖称</a>：“您现在可以在支持的平台上添加您的 Threads 个人资料链接来验证您的身份。”</p><p>这些只是 Meta 在过去几周推出的最新功能。该公司本月早些时候宣布， <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/threads-is-getting-a-web-version-and-a-search-function-in-the-next-few-weeks-101220107.html">急需的网络版本</a>即将推出，首次提供桌面使用以及适当的搜索功能。其他发布后添加的功能包括<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/threads-adds-a-chronological-feed-as-twitter-burns-to-the-ground-152817251.html">按时间顺序排列的提要</a>以及对<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/first-big-threads-update-for-ios-helps-you-see-new-followers-195035774.html">关注列表进行排序</a>和查看喜欢的帖子的功能。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/threads-now-lets-you-share-posts-directly-to-instagram-dms-201857138.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/threads-now-lets-you-share-posts-directly-to-instagram-dms-201857138.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> cd00ce46-93ba-4001-9566-d41179d7d7cc</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 09 Aug 2023 20:18:57 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691612338</ingested><modified> 2023-08-09T20:19:18+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="984" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/45ca1f40-36ec-11ee-adfd-c30bdef0ffd8" width="1638"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="984" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/45ca1f40-36ec-11ee-adfd-c30bdef0ffd8" width="1638"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Meta]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Screenshots of two phones showing Threads' new "Send on Instagram" feature. Left pane: pop-up menu showing options for where to post. Right pane: list of Instagram contacts to send it.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Meta Threads: Send to Instagram]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[8BitDo’s lat